    <item>
      <title>PSG Beats Marseille 2-1 in Thrilling Derby</title>
      <link>https://redsportsbetting.pages.dev/news/psg-marseille-review/</link>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 Jul 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://redsportsbetting.pages.dev/news/psg-marseille-review/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Paris Saint-Germain claimed a hard-fought 2-1 victory over Marseille in this weekend&amp;rsquo;s Classique, delighting home fans with a strong second-half performance.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;match-summary&#34;&gt;Match Summary&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;The match started evenly, with both sides testing each other&amp;rsquo;s defenses in the opening minutes. PSG broke the deadlock just before half-time, and doubled their lead early in the second half. Marseille pulled one back late on, but couldn&amp;rsquo;t find an equalizer.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;what-this-means-for-the-table&#34;&gt;What This Means for the Table&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;This result strengthens PSG&amp;rsquo;s position at the top, while Marseille will look to bounce back in their next fixture.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
